com.orsoncharts.data.xyz

Class XYZSeriesCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orsoncharts.data.AbstractDataset3D
      • com.orsoncharts.data.xyz.XYZSeriesCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Dataset3D, XYZDataset, java.io.Serializable

    public class XYZSeriesCollection
extends AbstractDataset3D
implements XYZDataset, java.io.Serializable
    A collection of XYZSeries objects (implements the XYZDataset interface so that it can be used as a source of data for an XYZRenderer on an XYZPlot).

    NOTE: This class is serializable, but the serialization format is subject to change in future releases and should not be relied upon for persisting instances of this class.
    See Also:
